description:
Enjoy the calm of underwater biomes, magnificence of horses and playfulness of dogs & cats! Collection includes special video puzzles.

Puzzle Galaxy: Animal Album adds 54 NEW jigsaw puzzles with cats, dogs, horses and ocean life:

• 18 puzzles with friendly Cats & Dogs
• 18 puzzles with swift Horses
• 18 puzzles with fascinating Ocean Life
name: Puzzle Galaxy: Animal Album - 54 new puzzles
